<HEAD>Julie Andrews Special Wins Four Emmys In Early Presentations</HEAD>
<HEAD>With AM-Emmys Bjt</HEAD>
<DATELINE>PASADENA, Calif. (AP) </DATELINE>
<TEXT>
   The ABC musical special ``Julie Andrews
... The Sound of Christmas'' won four Emmys, and CBS captured 16
early awards in technical and craft categories of the 40th Annual
